cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper focuses on the convergence rate of training recurrent neural networks, which is a topic closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the use of ReLU activations, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
